reviewText: Excellent visually but lacks pace required to hold the attention of most.

The videos cover a lot of information quickly and the interview footage was awesome! There were some things that I'm surprised didn't make it to the screen; the "angry alligator" AGENA malfunction being one. There were some things that I had never seen too, which was was cool; training stuff. Overall, very much worth the price and a valued new addition to my space collection.
